Quote: Mist Preservation Society Inc. - for rat control on the Mist Scenic Reserve on the northern Coromandel Peninsula. The 240ha Mist Scenic Reserve hosts the Moehau Beetle and the Coromandel striped gecko. Kiwis are also present. Up to $84,439.
